Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.57,0:00:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閃閃發亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奶奶買的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那時候卻只能用姊姊用過的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背起來去那邊的穿衣鏡看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華 要去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.69,0:00:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去散步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.41,0:01:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的村子 是個悠閒自在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這個春天開始 我就會成為村子裡面唯一一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.47,0:01:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閃閃發亮的一年級生
Comment: 0,0:00:00.99,0:00:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========OP================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.81,0:01:43.36,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}このあたりイチバン見晴らしの良いあの木に登って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.53,0:01:51.03,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}あの子が笑う 無邪気に笑う 夢を見る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.55,0:02:15.43,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}空を泳いだ魚の向こうじっと目を凝らせば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.77,0:02:22.44,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}町の隅っこ色褪せてゆく日々がある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:26.65,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ゆびきりしたままで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:29.61,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}サヨナラしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:38.62,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}果たされる日を待ってこの木に宿るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:42.71,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何回も繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:46.88,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そのたび涙する
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:50.51,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}止まって動き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:54.93,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そのすべてを確かめるように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:03:02.98,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ほら やまびこが聞こえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.81,0:01:43.36,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}爬上這一帶視野最美的那棵樹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.53,0:01:51.03,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}孩子笑了 笑得天真無邪 她看到了夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.55,0:02:15.43,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}定定地盯著空中暢遊的魚兒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.77,0:02:22.44,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}小鎮每個角落裡漸漸褪色的日子浮現出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:26.65,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}打勾勾上吊百年不變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:29.61,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即使分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:38.62,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}等待約定實現的心情也寄託在這棵樹上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:42.71,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一遍一遍地重複
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:46.88,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每次都止不住淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:50.51,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}停下來又繼續走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:54.93,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}彷彿是要印證這一切似的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:03:02.98,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}山間回音響不絕 妳說是不是呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.99,0:00:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:08.44,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1085.066,561.866)}{\c&HBE90F6&}成為了一年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 蓮華已經起來了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼把書包背起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,書包就是用來背的 戴頭上是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是那個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也很趕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔喔 好多草莓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這果醬是姊姊昨天做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出門要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去小學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入學式是明天喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是上小學的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姊 我撿到傳說中的劍了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是根棍子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.01,0:04:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是棍子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.72,0:04:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這重量 這樹枝 分明就是傳說中的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 妳剛才說它是樹枝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做路標
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就算迷路也可以回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才到這裡 就算妳一個人也可以回到家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姊不懂呀 天有不測之風雲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 妳們兩個怎麼出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華說想在入學式之前去學校看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,練習彩排
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 所以連書包都背上了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.09,0:04:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏夏 看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔喔 這不是傳說中的劍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用這個做好路標了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真虧妳知道那東西的名字呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:04:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是我告訴她的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是妳教的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也準備要去學校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可以帶蓮華一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有東西要收拾 要去東京呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好呀影姊 東京的高中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 巴士來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華 給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零用錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是車費 四月開始就要買兒童票了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 是哥哥 什麼時候上來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天氣也好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天開始就要自己注意不要坐過站了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華開始上學之後就要買定期票了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會買定期票給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天開始請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,書包扣子要好好扣上呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果裡面有書就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後上學習慣就不會了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.93,0:07:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們都很習慣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從小學開始已經在這上了七年學了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是六年呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海又回到一年級了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是國中一年級好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏夏的入學式也是明天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 雖然在畢業的地方入學感覺有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不要叫我小小鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入學式要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.25,0:07:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯… 要聽校長致辭 新生點名 唱完校歌就完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會點到我的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宮內蓮華同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華… 同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 感覺好成熟的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被點到的話要怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然要回答 那麼要彩排一下我的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏夏 麻煩叫一下我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 我想妳叫得成熟一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宮內蓮華同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再嚴肅一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宮內蓮華大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再正經一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宮內蓮華殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然妳大概已經知道了 這裡是教室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,門牌上還寫著加法算式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是國二 夏海是國一 哥哥是國三
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 小蓮也來了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓮不能進教室呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:08:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不能進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待一下明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:09:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去的時候我會叫妳的 先去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,書包放這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓮 那邊的水桶是用來接漏雨的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周圍地板都腐爛了 走太近的話會掉下去喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.76,0:09:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 到現在為止還沒有出現過陷進地板的笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不到那邊的路標了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的能成為一年生嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.99,0:00:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(partb)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要去東京了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺有點緊張呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東京好厲害呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對蓮華來說好像早了點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下次回來的時候 照張東京塔的照片給妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姊帶照相機了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒照相機的話照不了照片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然能照囉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有這部手機呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姊什麼時候買手機了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了方便聯繫買給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去東京的話果然還是得有部手機呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有手機的話照相什麼的什麼都可以做了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都可以做…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我要讓全世界的鯨魚變成能在天上飛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 並不是什麼都可以做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:12:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日影 沒有漏帶東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手帕和紙巾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題啦 仔細檢查過沒有漏東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有記得好好吃飯喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電車來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華 我走了之後寂寞的時候不要哭喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題 不會哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 蓮華那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1an8}影姊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1an8}影姊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還說不會寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1an8}影姊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘記拿手機啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.15,0:12:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快停下快停下 我的手機…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才買還沒握熱過的啊 我的手機 手機…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日影走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後幫她把手機寄過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我們回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尺寸怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不太確定 感覺剛剛好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好呀 有新的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再大一點後姊姊長高了的話 我的就讓給妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹的舊衣服！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法吧 我比妳長得更高
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過小蓮也入學了 我也有學妹了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓮會不會叫我學姊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊 把那邊的漫畫拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在準備明天的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我幫妳拿入學式的衣服過來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊 那是 訂製時裝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:15.57,Default,NTP,270,0,0,,{\fs48}haute couture
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是訂製時裝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是訂製時裝嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,訂製時裝是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 姊姊也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 定期票
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然明天我和爸爸媽媽應該會開車送妳去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還是在我忘記之前給妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我想一個人去上學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.07,0:14:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 不不 一個人就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:14:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天已經練習過了所以沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 那差不多該睡覺了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:16:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路標快要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早 蓮華
