Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是祝賀一年級生的花喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 小蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1an8}夏海 蓮華 祝賀妳們入學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 這是蓮華的座位喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐吧坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入學式差不多要開始了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年生 宮內蓮華同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
